title: RARE Disney Channel Movie - Bejewelled (1991)
description:
Looked for this movie for a long time and finally found it. Quality is pretty good for a old TV rip. If you&#039;ve never heard of this movie you can get a preview by going to the 1:50 mark of this Youtube video

The made-for-cable Bejewelled stars Emma Samms as a museum curator. Entrusted with collection of valuable jewels, she heads to London. Here she is obligated to fend off any number of potential thieves. It is also up to her to determine whom she can trust and whom she can not. Dennis Lawson, Jade Maigri, Aeryk Egan, Dirk Benedict costar.
